    <date month="February" year="1989"></date>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo describes an experimental method by which the Simple Network Management Protocol (SNMP) can be used over Ethernet MAC layer framing instead of the Internet UDP/IP protocol stack.  This specification is useful for LAN based network elements that support no higher layer protocols beyond the MAC sub-layer.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
